{"tid":1328919,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]Gundam Battle Operation 2 [42] 721 香港需要你 Gundam Pilot","createTime":"2019-07-18T05:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:18:36.000Z","uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb1ee350e2dd136cbf9b0405602bcef3b7194de","tid":1328919,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/89/17e7a37039a9731c2b4e9ba4bb10cbp5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F89%2F17e7a37039a9731c2b4e9ba4bb10cbp5.JPG&h=d7e985a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwgc5MS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbwgc5MS.png&h=6d45a129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sazezFe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsazezFe.png&h=565ebb6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日任<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGnapyZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGnapyZ.png&h=0afdd444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下格團團規(<span style=\"color: red;\">違規者踢</span>)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1.3日唔上就踢，日日清<br />\n(上唔到請講聲，冇人知你幾時棄game)<br />\n2.理性討論<br />\n3.下格歐洲人<br />\n4.尊重</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=b176c792\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=e4e583cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=f2526078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新手注意</span></span><br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QV6wq3t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV6wq3t.png&h=316827ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakrXxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=e06922a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>FAQ</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解我成日斷線</strong><br />\nA. 為己為人, <del>自殺</del> 對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 間中會遇到隱形敵人/無敵/黑畫面, 係咪有外掛?</strong><br />\nA. <del>掛你老母</del> 有咁嘅情況其實係Lag 機引致, 官方已經公佈咗短期內會有update 去解決問題 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似已經fix咗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?</strong><br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?</strong><br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解無得同朋友一齊開房玩</strong><br />\nA. 除咗Ranking mode之外, 其他2個mode 都可以邀朋友<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣用支援炮擊</strong><br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?</strong><br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣放炸彈</strong><br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n     2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n     3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按O 裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)</strong><br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n (Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？</strong><br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得 <br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點樣出反格</strong><br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬</strong><br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Q. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?</strong><br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>手製SETTING建議</strong><br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, One.For.All, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡"},{"pid":"7786a04871330e5c1e4290fa14832ecfc9c4acc2","tid":1328919,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"又唔開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日新機係<br />\nG-Line standard armor<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b563242eb7d0f5a986390b613500911092e8c0a","tid":1328919,"uid":17459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"G奶加特林碎擊炮型 啲豆幾正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34bf61b3aedc53a544589547b90f796e5ae8d6f","tid":1328919,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34ii1mf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34ii1mf.jpg&h=e7328ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱先睇到原來有披露返中獎率<br />\n仲以為笨大咁大膽唔講<img src=\"/assets/